Welcome to a world where yellow thing-a-majigs reign supreme, giants and petites live in harmony, and corals roam across the night sky. It makes absolutely no sense. 
04/26/22 -- 7:53 A.M.
seems this normal ol wooden plains level got flooded by something! best to watch out for the flopping fish, for they can still harm you!
Re-issuing old levels, so I don't have to make levels! Lazy, ain't it? (Though this will only happen to levels that are old and I have no plans on doing anything with)

so much sand, with so many coins found deep under such! think you can unearth enough for a nice three extra lives?
don't forget to check what's in the bricks as well!
